'''圣乌苏拉圣殿'''（St. Ursula）位于[[德国|德国]][[科隆|科隆]]，兴建在古罗马墓地废墟上；据说有与圣乌苏拉有关的11,000名处女埋葬在那里<ref name="world and its people">{{cite book
  |last = Dunton
  |first = Larkin
  |authorlink = 
  |title = The World and Its People
  |url = https://archive.org/details/worldanditspeop05duntgoog
  |publisher = Silver, Burdett
  |series = 
  |year = 1896
  |page = [https://archive.org/details/worldanditspeop05duntgoog/page/n193 185]}}</ref>。该堂有一个令人印象深刻的[[圣物箱|圣物箱]]，用该墓地的尸骨制成。它是科隆12座罗曼式教堂之一<ref>[http://www.sacred-destinations.com/germany/cologne-romanesque-churches.htm Sacred Destinations:] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sacred-destinations.com/germany/cologne-romanesque-churches.htm |date=20110609200627 }},''The Twelve Romanesque Churches of Cologne'' (accessed 2011-04-17)</ref>，1920年6月25日指定为[[宗座圣殿|宗座圣殿]]。
